                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">little things like this.....
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://www.vanguardsoh.com/forums/showthread.php?threadid=8405" target="_blank">http://www.vanguardsoh.com/forums/showthread.php?threadid=8405</a>
<br />

<br />

<br />
A simple question.  A member of the Vanguard community posts a question about game design ideas and what it takes to break into the business....
<br />

<br />
Not only does a member of Microsofts staff pipe in, the man himself, Brad McQuaid stops in to lend some helpful information.
<br />

<br />
THATS what im talking about and what is worth of "faith" and hype, imho.  Such a simple act goes such a long way in earning respect.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Ungzaba Bruja, 70 Wizard, Vazaelle
