<br />
They changed your complaint Culby.  There are now bindstones at the portal keeps in the frontiers, so you can release right back to there if you want.  It still takes a while to get back to where the action is, since the portal keeps are a ways out, but at least it's no longer "Pop in from death at the town nearest the portal keep, run for 10 minutes to reach the portal keep, wait for 5 minutes for the portal ceremony, then run for 10 minutes to return to battle";  Now it's closer to "pop in from death at the portal keep, trigger the ceremony instantly, and spend 10 minutes running back to battle."
<br />

<br />
Much more palatable, really.  Though a lot of folks now have issues with the keep-centricness of RvR.  They're never happy, I tell you.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
