                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Shadowrun?  Sorry, can't see that as a real head turner myself.
<br />

<br />
Probably most people will say the same about the one I'd like to see: ShadowWorld (the one done by the old I.C.E. - Iron Crown Enterprises). Or for those that followed it Kulthea.
<br />

<br />
The world was fairly generic in some terms, but had a nice blend of Tech for those that like to see them together. Not enough to push the envelope though.  Of course I am biased having run a campaign or two in the world.  Even worked really hard to expand one of the continent modules to a long term game.  Never did quite get it finished though, we kept losing players over time and with work it never quite got into the really good parts I had planned.  <img src="images/smiles/icon_confused.gif" alt="icon_confused.gif" border="0" />
<br />

<br />
Some new races, mostly standard though. <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Nysa Stargazer, Phantasmist of the 61st Veil
<br />
Follower of Erollisi Marr
<br />
